{"id":15465,"date":"2024-10-16T10:58:00","date_gmt":"2024-10-16T05:28:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=15465"},"modified":"2024-10-17T12:13:57","modified_gmt":"2024-10-17T06:43:57","slug":"diwali-light-decoration-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/diwali-light-decoration-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Stunning Diwali Light Decoration Ideas For A Sparkly Festive Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Decorating your home for Diwali is now super easy! These 5 Diwali light decoration ideas will make your home a happy festive space.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The festival of lights brings a mesmerising view outside our windows filled with beautiful lights and fireworks, but there\u2019s so much to do back at home. Right from having an intricate diya decoration spread out across the home to stunning Diwali light decorations that bring more life to your home, Diwali is all about tuning into the festivities with warmth, light and love. And this article takes you through 5 such stunning Diwali light decoration ideas that stand out and make for a refreshing welcome to your home this festive season. Without further ado, let\u2019s dive right in!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Diwali Decoration Ideas For Your Balcony Space In Indian Apartments<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Have a balcony that is plain and dull? It&#8217;s time to deck it up with some Diwali light decorations. Bring out those fairy lights that you have stored away in your attic and set them up. If you take a look at this balcony, it&#8217;s beautifully dressed with fairy lights from top to bottom creating a parade of light. This balcony also has a bookshelf that has been outlined with fairy lights which is an excellent way to decorate a balcony space. Cut out birds and stars and hang them together on a string to create a chime of their own to make this balcony ready for Diwali decoration.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131740\/diwali-lighting-ideas-in-balcony-with-fairy-lights.jpg\" alt=\"Diwali lighting ideas in balcony with fairy lights\" class=\"wp-image-15471\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131740\/diwali-lighting-ideas-in-balcony-with-fairy-lights.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131740\/diwali-lighting-ideas-in-balcony-with-fairy-lights-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131740\/diwali-lighting-ideas-in-balcony-with-fairy-lights-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131740\/diwali-lighting-ideas-in-balcony-with-fairy-lights-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Decorate furniture with Diwali light decoration<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Easy DIY Diwali Decoration Ideas | Budget Friendly Diwali Home Decoration Ideas | DesignCafe\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/vTvjNacEhNs?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Elegant Diwali Lighting Ideas And Floating Diyas For The Perfect Festive Vibe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want a Diwali lighting idea that stands out from the rest then this one is just perfect. This living room features a beautiful drop-down decorative pendant light that shines through the space aesthetically. Fairy lights dropped down from the large bay windows add a touch of spark to the space. Copper bowls filled with red rose petals and floating diyas add up as the centre of attraction as the perfect Diwali decoration ideas. This living room has a floor-to-ceiling unit with shelves that have LED strip lighting \u2014 ideal to amplify the Diwali spirit.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131723\/diwali-light-decoration-in-small-living-room-with-petals-and-diyas.jpg\" alt=\"Diwali light decoration in small living room with-petals and diyas\" class=\"wp-image-15469\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131723\/diwali-light-decoration-in-small-living-room-with-petals-and-diyas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131723\/diwali-light-decoration-in-small-living-room-with-petals-and-diyas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131723\/diwali-light-decoration-in-small-living-room-with-petals-and-diyas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131723\/diwali-light-decoration-in-small-living-room-with-petals-and-diyas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Designer pendant orbs for Diwali lighting ideas<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Candle-Lit Delight As Diwali Light Decoration Home<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Remember all those candles that you got for Christmas and had them stowed away into boxes? Well, it&#8217;s time to bring them out. This Diwali, use candles to decorate your home. Candles can be arranged around a beautiful flower or colour rangoli design. Additionally, you can use a variety of scented candles if you are big on the aroma.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131641\/diwali-light-decoration-for-balcony-with-candles.jpg\" alt=\"Diwali light decoration home in balcony with candles and bowl filled with petals\" class=\"wp-image-15466\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131641\/diwali-light-decoration-for-balcony-with-candles.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131641\/diwali-light-decoration-for-balcony-with-candles-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131641\/diwali-light-decoration-for-balcony-with-candles-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131641\/diwali-light-decoration-for-balcony-with-candles-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Diwali light decoration home featuring pretty candles<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Diwali Lights Decoration With Lanterns, Petals And Candles<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A unique Diwali light decoration can steal the show &#8211; like this table. It&#8217;s neatly decorated with glass and copper lanterns of different shades that bring an antique yet festive look into your home. Rose petals have been scattered here and there to bring in a fresh yet vibrant vibe. Candles in small glasses have been placed on the table which brings an elegant look to the Diwali celebrations.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131730\/diwali-lighting-design-with-lanterns-candles-petals.jpg\" alt=\"How to make diwali lamp - diwali lighting design with lanterns, candles and petals\" class=\"wp-image-15470\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131730\/diwali-lighting-design-with-lanterns-candles-petals.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131730\/diwali-lighting-design-with-lanterns-candles-petals-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131730\/diwali-lighting-design-with-lanterns-candles-petals-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131730\/diwali-lighting-design-with-lanterns-candles-petals-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Tea light candles in lanterns for Diwali lights decoration<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Quick and Stunning Diwali Decor Ideas for 2024 | DesignCafe\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/9LBIjxXgcII?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Table Makeover With Special Diwali Light Decorations<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Have a coffee table sitting alone in plain sight? Give it a fancy makeover with candles, oil lamps and copper\/silver bowls. Place the copper\/silver bowl on the table and fill it with pretty flower petals in different colours. Place tea light candles or small diyas inside the bowl and let them float in water. Onto the next! Use medium-sized diyas to surround your coffee table. This light decoration will look stunning and won\u2019t take much of your time.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131703\/diwali-light-decoration-for-coffee-table-with-diyas.jpg\" alt=\"Diwali light decoration for coffee table with diyas and a bowl filled with water, petals\" class=\"wp-image-15467\" style=\"width:838px;height:503px\" width=\"838\" height=\"503\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131703\/diwali-light-decoration-for-coffee-table-with-diyas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131703\/diwali-light-decoration-for-coffee-table-with-diyas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131703\/diwali-light-decoration-for-coffee-table-with-diyas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/13131703\/diwali-light-decoration-for-coffee-table-with-diyas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 838px) 100vw, 838px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Diwali decoration ideas with elegant decor for your coffee table<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Make the most of these simple Diwali light decoration ideas for your home this Diwali and bring some light, love and festive vibe to your home. Looking to add #MoreRoomForCelebration? <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">Connect with our experts at DesignCafe<\/a> to design the home of your dreams!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Need more Diwali decor ideas? Check out our other festive special blogs:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/25-best-diwali-decoration-ideas-for-home\/\">Top 25 Diwali Decor Ideas<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/diwali-decoration-ideas-for-living-room\/\">Living Room Decor Ideas For Diwali<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/7-diy-diwali-diya-decoration-ideas-for-home\/\">7 Diwali Diya Decor Ideas<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/diwali-lighting-ideas-for-balcony\/\">Diwali Light Decoration Ideas For Balcony<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs About Diwali Light Decor<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1. What are some traditional Diwali lighting options for homes?&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Traditional Diwali lighting options for homes include diyas, candles, oil lamps, and string lights. These timeless choices will create a warm and inviting ambiance.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2. How can I decorate my entrance with lights for Diwali?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To decorate your entrance with lights for Diwali, consider using string lights to outline the doorway, place diyas or lanterns along the pathway, and add a beautiful rangoli with diyas around it for a festive touch.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3. Are there any eco-friendly lighting options for Diwali?&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, there are multiple eco-friendly lighting options for Diwali. You can use LED lights, solar-powered lanterns, and recycled or biodegradable materials to reduce your environmental footprint.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4. What are some creative ways to use string lights for Diwali decoration?&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>String lights offer creative versatility for Diwali decoration. You can use them to create unique patterns, hang them in curtains, or wrap them around objects to illuminate your space in a unique way.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>5. How can I incorporate traditional oil lamps (diyas) into my Diwali decor?&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Incorporating traditional oil lamps (diyas) into your Diwali decor is easy and fun. Place diyas on windowsills, balconies, or in decorative rangolis on the floor. They bring a traditional charm to your celebrations.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>6. How can I make my Diwali lighting unique and personalized?&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Personalise your Diwali lighting by creating handmade lanterns, scented candles, or string lights with colours and designs that resonate with your style and preferences.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>7. What are some trendy Diwali lighting ideas for 2023?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Trendy Diwali lighting ideas for 2023 include using LED fairy lights in innovative designs, such as shaping them into flowers or draping them on indoor plants, and embracing unique pendant lights and chandeliers to create a stylish and contemporary atmosphere.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content